        <h4>How does the Partner plan work?</h4>
        <p>When you sign a contract with one of our verified partner contractors, you automatically get full access to all platform features for the duration of your project. This ensures you can fully visualize and plan your renovation before work begins.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h4>What happens to my credits if I don't use them?</h4>
        <p>Credits never expire! Buy them when you need them and use them at your own pace. They're perfect for one-time projects or occasional design needs.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h4>Can I switch between plans?</h4>
        <p>Yes! You can upgrade or downgrade your plan at any time. If you upgrade, you'll be credited for the unused portion of your current plan.</p>
      </div>
